          This is the backing field for CommonToken.getChannel() and CommonToken.setChannel(int).

        • source

          Pair<A,B> source
          This is the backing field for CommonToken.getTokenSource() and CommonToken.getInputStream().

          These properties share a field to reduce the memory footprint of CommonToken. Tokens created by a CommonTokenFactory from the same source and input stream share a reference to the same Pair containing these values.

        • text

          String text
          This is the backing field for CommonToken.getText() when the token text is explicitly set in the constructor or via CommonToken.setText(java.lang.String).
          See Also:
